title: Can't login to login queue
body:
Help?
Is it just something with NA rn?

replies.body: Yeah!  NA is currently undergoing maintenance, but some players are failing to login as a result.  We are posting updates on the [maintenance thread](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/live-incident-breakdown-na/PTQej3Tj-june-7th-na-ranked-disabled-for-live-maintenance) for now, and hope to get you back in on the double!
